doctype html
html(lang='en', ng-app='application')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')

        title zChat

        link(rel='stylesheet', href='tether/dist/css/tether.min.css')
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css')
        link(href='css/app.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

        script(src='jquery/dist/jquery.min.js')
        script(src='tether/dist/js/tether.min.js')
        script(src='bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js')
        script(src='socket.io/socket.io.js')

body

    #enterChatModal.modal.fade(role='dialog', aria-labelledby='myModalLabel', aria-hidden='false')
        .modal-dialog(role='document')
            .modal-content
                .modal-body
                    .form-group
                        input#name.form-control(type='text', autofocus, placeholder="Your name:")
                    button#enter.btn.btn-primary(type='button') Enter

    .row
        .col-xs-3
            ul.list-group
                h1 Rooms
                li.list-group-item.active
                    span.label.label-default.label-pill.pull-xs-right 14
                    | Cras justo odio
                li.list-group-item
                    span.label.label-default.label-pill.pull-xs-right 2
                    | Dapibus ac facilisis in
                li.list-group-item
                    span.label.label-default.label-pill.pull-xs-right 1
                    | Morbi leo risus
        .col-xs-6
            h1
                .btn-group(data-toggle='buttons')
                    label.btn.btn-primary.active
                        input#option2(type='radio', name='options', autocomplete='off')
                        | Public msg
                    label.btn.btn-primary
                        input#option3(type='radio', name='options', autocomplete='off')
                        | Private msg
            #messages
                each val in [{ name: "john", postedDate: new Date() }, { name: "john", postedDate: new Date() }, { name: "john", postedDate: new Date() }, { name: "john", postedDate: new Date() }, { name: "john", postedDate: new Date() }, { name: "john", postedDate: new Date() }]
                    .media
                        a.pull-left(href='#')
                            img.media-object(src='http://placehold.it/64x64', alt='')
                        .media-body
                            h4.media-heading.name #{val.name}
                                small.posted-date #{val.postedDate}
                            | Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin commodo. Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus viverra turpis. Fusce condimentum nunc ac nisi vulputate fringilla. Donec lacinia congue felis in faucibus.
            .input-group
                input#messageInput.form-control(type='text', placeholder="Recipient's username", aria-describedby='basic-addon2')
                span#basic-addon2.input-group-addon send
        .col-xs-3
            ul.list-group
                h1 Rooms
                li.list-group-item Cras justo odio
                li.list-group-item.active Dapibus ac facilisis in
                li.list-group-item Morbi leo risus
                li.list-group-item Porta ac consectetur ac
                li.list-group-item Vestibulum at eros
